{"tid":1869624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"罷工護士準備好面對秋後算帳　復工將主動加入 Dirty Team　聞罷工失敗淚崩：迫唔到政府封關，救唔到市民","createTime":"2020-02-08T09:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T10:07:34.000Z","uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3db2e306bf87b98d0a25d38b65ad176d05f4852d","tid":1869624,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E8%AD%B7%E5%A3%AB%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E7%A7%8B%E5%BE%8C%E7%AE%97%E5%B8%B3-%E5%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5-dirty-team-%E8%81%9E%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E6%B7%9A%E5%B4%A9-%E8%BF%AB%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C-%E6%95%91%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%25B8%25B3-%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5-dirty-team-%25E8%2581%259E%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25B4%25A9-%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C-%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=ad4a19da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%25B8%25B3-%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5-dirty-team-%25E8%2581%259E%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25B4%25A9-%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C-%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%2F&h=d060b7da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E8%AD%B7%E5%A3%AB%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E7%A7%8B%E5%BE%8C%E7%AE%97%E5%B8%B3-%E5%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5-dirty-team-%E8%81%9E%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E6%B7%9A%E5%B4%A9-%E8%BF%AB%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C-%E6%95%91%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91/</a><br />\n<br />\n盧護士謂自己的崗位是最安全的康復病房，但復工後她會<span style=\"color: red;\">主動加入 Dirty Team</span>，照顧確診病人。<br />\n<br />\n「當年沙士已經好想去幫手，但嗰時經驗未夠。」現在的她已去過急症病房進修，覺得是時候出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n無論投票結果如何，她不忍撇下同事，早已決定明天復工。「我唔可以拋低病房入面做埋我地嗰份嘅同事。其實佢地都支持罷工，但要照顧病人維持最基本服務。有啲平時坐 office 嘅上司唔方便出聲，而家出嚟落手落腳幫我地。」<br />\n<br />\n「點解政府唔聽民意？唔聽專家意見？」她不認為罷工失敗，香港史上首次醫護罷工令市民見到政府的真面目。<br />\n<br />\n她說醫護會用行動回應「逃兵」的指控。「怕死係人之常情，關鍵係面對難關時點樣衡量同決定，我好多同事都喺 Dirty Team。」由昔日沙士到今日罷工，她說醫護行動的首要考量都是市民。「我地冇調轉頭。」<br />\n<br />\n當工會正式宣布罷工結束，她忍不住淚崩：「罷工又話我地累市民；唔罷工啲高官又縮哂沙。我地始終迫唔到政府封關，救唔到香港市民。」<br />\n<br />\n睇你班垃圾幾撚犯賤<br />\n唔resign都算啦<br />\n趕住去投胎咩"},{"pid":"2f354d2873c9b884472696d926f81fee6d561ddb","tid":1869624,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:31:45.000Z","msg":"奴性咁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9902da0c5010088387b9b65d00fb2ac9183fce2","tid":1869624,"uid":45914,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5fc690941aaf9caafe9c7a32404f206d58d3738","tid":1869624,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:34:12.000Z","msg":"真係勸罷咗工嘅醫院謀定後路<br />\n你哋個record花撚晒<br />\n仆街工會累死人"},{"pid":"92d9504fa365a9697aafcceb4686c4c7